{
  "stem": "17821.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was their main office in Europe because from Paris, they managed all the other countries who-- that rented Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer films.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then since I was interested in languages, I studied some languages on my own.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And eventually, my job became quite a different one.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I, I was given a secretary of my own.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I dictated my mail to her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I supervised the dubbing languages.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That is to say, at that time in Europe, there was a situation where the, the different governments made a law that films could not be distributed in the same way.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Only, only one main one could be shown in the capital.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The others all had to be dubbed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had a specialist, a very well-educated French woman, who translated the American texts into French.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had to pass on it that it was a correct translation.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We also had German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I supervised the German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had Spanish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I supervised Spanish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Italian, I didn't know the language, but I could judge it from my Spanish and from my Latin.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I minored in Latin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Hungarian-- I was doing Hungarian because, in the meantime, I had studied Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I was really-- that was my job, supervising dubbing in different languages.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
